# 📈 Step 9: SEO + Performance (VERY IMPORTANT 💥)

### ✅ SEO

* Use proper tags:

```html
<title>Business Website</title>
<meta name="description" content="Modern business solutions" />
```

* Use semantic HTML:

```html
<header> <main> <section> <footer>
```

---

### ⚡ Performance Tips

* Lazy load images
* Use `loading="lazy"`
* Optimize images (WebP)
* Minimize JS bundles

